      <title>中國3月鐵礦石進口量小幅成長，鋼材出口量創8年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週五海關數據顯示，中國3月鐵礦石進口量年增約0.5%，因預計春節假期後需求將回升，因為鋼鐵製造商通常會提高產量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中國最大貿易展上的關鍵字是“低價”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[從週一開始，外國買家將湧入中國最大的貿易博覽會的廣闊大廳，尋找中國商品的交易，美國和歐洲政府抱怨這些商品正在湧入全球市場。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
